tip_battle.title: Cúchulainn (Incubus)
tip_battle.message:
• -The more heroes with Record Synergy in the party, the more the enemy's resistance to break debuffs and elemental damage will be lowered, and the more damage you will deal to them.
  • -Uses strong dark and poison attacks.
  • -Uses attacks that ignore resistances and Poison, Slow, Stop, and Doom.
  • -Uses Incubus Gravija, which ignores resistances, Mirror Image, and Magic Barrier, dealing damage proportional to the current HP of those hit.
  • -Uses Incubus Unholy Darkness, which ignores Magic Barrier, and lowers the Doom countdown.
  • -If the fight drags on without you reducing the HP of the enemy enough, they strike the entire party with Incubus Dead End, which can break the damage cap, ignores resistances, and Instantly KO.
